# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok toyota said friday it 's planning a new level of disclosure about car problems beyond what the automaker is legally required to reveal as it seeks to rebuild consumer trust .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Toyota"))
      :ARG1 (p / plan-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (d / disclose-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (p2 / problem
                        :topic (c2 / car))
                  :mod (l / level
                        :ARG1-of (n2 / new-01))
                  :mod (b / beyond
                        :op1 (d2 / disclose-01
                              :ARG0 (c3 / company
                                    :ARG0-of (m / make-01
                                          :ARG1 (a / automobile)))
                              :ARG1-of (r / require-01
                                    :ARG0 (l2 / law)
                                    :ARG2 c3
                                    :time (s2 / seek-01
                                          :ARG0 c3
                                          :ARG1 (r2 / rebuild-01
                                                :ARG0 c3
                                                :ARG1 (t / trust-01
                                                      :ARG0 (p3 / person
                                                            :ARG0-of (c4 / consume-01)))))))))
            :time (d3 / date-entity
                  :weekday (f / friday))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the united states on thursday welcomed reports that pakistan 's president pervez musharraf was ready to drop a demand for a referendum in the disputed territory of kashmir .
# ::alignments
(w / welcome-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "United"
                  :op2 "States"))
      :ARG1 (r / report-01
            :ARG1 (r2 / ready-02
                  :ARG1 (p / person
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Pervez"
                              :op2 "Musharraf")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c2 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Pakistan"))
                              :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
                  :ARG2 (d / drop-05
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (d2 / demand-01
                              :ARG0 p
                              :ARG1 (r3 / referendum
                                    :location (c3 / country-region
                                          :name (n4 / name
                                                :op1 "Kashmir")
                                          :ARG2-of (d3 / dispute-01)))))))
      :time (d4 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok chinese company tcl teamed with french company thomson tuesday in this capital of south china 's guangdong province to form the world largest television production joint venture .
# ::alignments
(p / partner-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Tcl")
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "China")))
      :ARG1 (c3 / company
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Thomson")
            :mod (c4 / country
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "France")))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday))
      :location (c5 / city
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / province
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Guangdong")
                        :location (s / south
                              :part-of c2))
                  :ARG2 (c6 / capital)))
      :purpose (f / form-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (v / venture
                  :mod (j / joint)
                  :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                        :ARG2 (l / large)
                        :ARG3 (m / most)
                        :ARG5 (w / world))
                  :mod (p3 / produce-01
                        :ARG1 (t2 / television)))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the u.n. security council arrived friday in ethiopia to begin a tour focusing on africa 's hotspots -- the war in darfur and its spillover into neighboring chad , fighting in somalia and efforts to bring peace to eastern congo .
# ::alignments
(a / arrive-01
      :ARG1 (o / organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Security"
                  :op2 "Council")
            :mod o
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "U.N."))
      :ARG4 (c / country
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Ethiopia"))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :purpose (b / begin-01
            :ARG0 o
            :ARG1 (t / tour-01
                  :ARG0 o
                  :ARG1 (h / hotspot
                        :poss (c2 / continent
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Africa"))
                        :example (a2 / and
                              :op1 (w / war-01
                                    :location (c3 / city
                                          :name (n5 / name
                                                :op1 "Darfur")))
                              :op2 (s / spill-over-02
                                    :ARG1 w
                                    :ARG2 (c4 / country
                                          :name (n6 / name
                                                :op1 "Chad")
                                          :ARG1-of (n7 / neighbor-01)))
                              :op3 (f2 / fight-01
                                    :location (c5 / country
                                          :name (n8 / name
                                                :op1 "Somalia")))
                              :op4 (e / effort-01
                                    :ARG1 (b2 / bring-01
                                          :ARG1 (p / peace)
                                          :ARG2 (w2 / world-region
                                                :name (n9 / name
                                                      :op1 "Eastern"
                                                      :op2 "Congo")))))))))

                                    :op1 "Procter"

            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "Willette")

            :ARG1 a2)

                  :op1 "Gamble"

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :ARG1-of (n5 / new-01))

                                          :ARG0 o
                                          :ARG1 o
                                          :ARG2 c)))
                        :ARG3 (t / thing
                              :ARG1-of (ii / important-01))))
            :mod (o2 / official))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday)))

# ::id 11 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :time (w / wednesday))
            :ARG0-of (p / provide-01
                  :ARG1 (e / evidence-01

                                    :mod (s3 / such))
                              :ARG1 (l2 / live-01))
                        :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                              :ARG2 (e2 / evidence-01

                                          :ARG2 (s4 / strong-02
                                                :ARG1 e2)
                                          :ARG3 (m / most)))
                              :ARG3 (s5 / some)))))
      :ARG1 (d / die-01
            :ARG1 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (r3 / reside-01
                        :ARG1 (s6 / state
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Massachusetts")))
                  :ARG1-of (h2 / have-quant-91
                        :ARG3 (l3 / less
                              :quant (n2 / nearly))))
            :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (h3 / heart-attack))
            :frequency (y2 / year
                  :mod (e3 / each))
            :time (s7 / since
                  :op1 (b / ban-01
                        :ARG0 p2

                        :location (a / and
